Class StreamingResponse

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.scvngr.levelup.core.net.AbstractResponse<InputStream>
      • com.scvngr.levelup.core.net.StreamingResponse

  • @LevelUpApi(contract=INTERNAL)
public class StreamingResponse
extends AbstractResponse<InputStream>
    An AbstractResponse that uses a streaming interface where the response data is read from a stream.
